snippet.title: Playdate Catalog - Games for August 2023 -  Smolitaire, Tartine's Show, Factory Farming, and more!
snippet.description:
Take a look at the amazing Playdate games that arrived in August 2023 on Catalog! 

These games can be purchased on-device or at https://play.date/games/catalog/

0:07 - To Dust
0:21 - Smolitaire
0:39 - Factory Farming
0:57 - The Crank Gym
1:13 - Ribbit Rabbit
1:31 - Soko
1:54 - Crank Tanks
2:13 - Crash Mole
2:30 - Play Dice
2:46 - The Tartine's Show

Games for Playdate can also be sideloaded and purchased from sites like Itch.io. 

Playdate is available for pre-order for $199 at https://play.date
